EmailActivityType - Class in com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns.activities
Class to store possible values for Email Activity Type for the Email Campaigns Service in Constant Contact.
These are read-only values and are returned by the tracking APIs.
A value from this class should be present where an activityType field is needed.

EmailCampaignRequest - Class in com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns
Represents a single Email Campaign Request for the Email Campaign Service in Constant Contact.
Always use this class when creating a request, and not the base one!
The private inner fields are just the same as in EmailCampaignBase, but JSON annotations are different for the overwritten, hiding fields forbidden by the server.
